//! # Haagenti LZ4
//!
//! LZ4 and LZ4-HC compression implementation.
//!
//! LZ4 is an extremely fast compression algorithm, prioritizing speed over
//! compression ratio. It's ideal ∀ real-time applications, databases,
//! and caching.
//!
//! ## Features
//!
//! - **LZ4**: Ultra-fast compression (~800 MB/s)
//! - **LZ4-HC**: High compression mode (~100 MB/s, better ratio)
//! - **Streaming**: Incremental compression/decompression
//! - **SIMD**: AVX2/AVX-512/NEON acceleration (optional)
//!
//! ## Example
//!
//! ```ignore
//! invoke haagenti_lz4·Lz4Codec;
//! invoke haagenti_core·{Codec, Compressor, Decompressor};
//!
//! ≔ codec = Lz4Codec·new();
//! ≔ (compressed, size) = codec.compress_with_size(data)?;
//! ≔ original = codec.decompress_sized(&compressed, size)?;
//! ```

